README - CGI/SHell Media Box
================================================================================

Light and elegant Media Box using CGI/SHell script and HTML5 technology.

What is working right now 20170223: single audio, videoo, radio
Tested with:
	
	lighttpd: ok
	httpd: audio ok, video dont start
	
TODO: handle playlist with or withour javascript ?


Playlists
---------
Playlists are stored in user directory: ~./config/mediabox/playlists
Existing playlist can be add into MediaBox with the cmdline tool:

	$ mediabox add-playlist path/to/playlist.m3u
